        "name": "纳西妲",
        "desc": "<p>深居净善宫的笼中之鸟，只能在梦中将世界尽收眼底。</p>",
        "iconUrl": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/11/01/47826599/f29490bddc56b4a6773b6c5003bbb853_9178865138637843993.png",
